title: AIIMS Kalyani Recruitment 2026 - Apply Online for 133 Senior Resident Posts
description: All India Institute of Medical Sciences (AIIMS Kalyani ) has declared the official notification for 2026. To fill up the vacancies for 133 Senior Resident Jobs. Those candidates who have qualified in the MBBS, MD/ MS, and DNB can grab this chance and apply for the AIIMS Kalyani Recruitment 2026 . Here, we included the age limit, selection process, salary structure, education details, application fee, and how to apply for these posts. Interested candidates can apply on or before the last date ...
